                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1429-18430508 t18430508-1429-punishment-30"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Baron Gurney.</hi>
